      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ATOMIC DIVA (1) sprung the lids and on speed throughout before being run over late when fourth (24.02) at Horsham over 410m. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Can make amends. VALLETTA PEARL (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at Warrnambool over 390m behind Penny Pinto (23.08) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Bold showing expected. DEMONIC SPIRIT (8) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at Healesville following on from a second place finish (19.93) there the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. One of the better chances. HELLO COOPER (6) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
